\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\pi}{4}\leq\phi\leq\frac{\pi}{2}$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Für das untere Limit 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi=\frac{\pi}{4}$
\end_inset

